  <acronym>PERICLESAPPI</acronym>
  <official_title>First Experiences With an Offline App (SPA; Smartphone Application) for Colonoscopy Preparation- PERICLES-I APP; Prospective Evaluations of Improvement of Colonocopy Preparation by Optimized Visualization (PERICLES)</official_title>
