  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Feasibility of an newly programmed offline application for smartphones (SPA, APP) for
      colonoscopy preparation offering a 5 day guidance prior colonoscopy containing dietary- and
      behavioral recommendation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      First feasibility testing of a newly programmed app/SPA for android system named Colopr-APP.
      It is an strictly offline working, autonomous system downloaded to the smartphone. It creates
      an 5-day guidance prior outpatient colonoscopy with dietary and behavior recommendations.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
